lead_paragraph: Russian sports minister Vitaly Mutko plans to meet an inspection  commission of the International Association of Athletics Federations (IAAF) in Moscow on Jan. 11, RIA news agency reported citing Mutko.

headline.print_headline: Russian Sports Minister to Meet International Athletics Commission on January 11: RIA
